	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yes, the Powerpak has 32k of ram set aside for save ram.  Whenever it sees any sort of write to the save ram, and when you press and hold reset for three seconds, it will prompt to save the ram to the Compact Flash.  With this rom, it prompts so it would seem the Powerpak is seeing the sram contents being written.

		

